{"tid":774764,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵人一齊睇下笑片輕鬆下","createTime":"2018-08-10T14:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T07:29:03.000Z","uid":62752,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4c6841dc9ee8a03ac03339dc1908ca69cd4756","tid":774764,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"講開經典笑片, 大多數諗起周星馳<br />\n外國經典笑片, 你又諗起咩人呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次簡左套 2009年既戲一齊睇,  Jim Carrey演既, <br />\n叫YES MAN, 香港版譯就叫「乜都得先生」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n套戲係講男主Jim Carrey有日加入左一個自助組織, 組織既宗旨係只可以對人地既問題答YES, 如果乜都答YES, Jim Carrey之後既人生會點走落去??<br />\n<br />\n如果呢排冇咩野做, <br />\n不如一齊睇戲輕鬆下, <br />\n又以戲會友, 一齊睇戲吹下水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上trailer一段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ly5q4rY6ShQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dly5q4rY6ShQ&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=704fada8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ly5q4rY6ShQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報名LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/KSpZItWbp1Ov15XI3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FKSpZItWbp1Ov15XI3&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=31c64ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/KSpZItWbp1Ov15XI3</a>"},{"pid":"4523b0caca9b4a449abd9bb08eb70245b91e31a1","tid":774764,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"報名"},{"pid":"dfc2d0a4581414d92e62b00c4df8a82fcd788458","tid":774764,"uid":62752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4523b0caca9b4a449abd9bb08eb70245b91e31a1","tid":774764,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite